{"tid":981513,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［可能係］香港最正既豆腐花","createTime":"2019-01-14T10:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T08:58:31.000Z","uid":221748,"like":25,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea678cdcdb9b4ad0d29bcab389b1c96af6c3fab","tid":981513,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"🇭🇰#香港捐窿捐罅記<br />\n介紹下一間幾好食既豆腐花先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前荃灣果兩間食店 互相做爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到豆腐花又出名左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係果兩間聽講都麻麻 所以之後兩個post 我會分別介紹兩間大埔出名既豆腐花店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比較一下傳統同新派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2p8PWzj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2p8PWzj.png&h=cd9ab58c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-<br />\n🥛熱豆腐花（$9）<br />\n一入口 幾重豆味 而且幾滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要係夠嫩 冇過火 亦都冇任何豆腐渣👍 <br />\n黃糖同糖水都係自己增加 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己中意幾甜就幾甜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDP7Jev.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDP7Jev.png&h=081f88cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過聽講以前個豆味係更重 不過宜家已經用唔同豆 所以差左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總結來說 以豆腐花來説幾高質 可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-<br />\n平均傷害：$9<br />\n<br />\nInstagram:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=za0r9j99p4z4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffoodkiller_dk%3Futm_source%3Dig_profile_share%26igshid%3Dza0r9j99p4z4&d=e3TO9ons5iEXHyTzMAd6wZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=1d70eff5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=za0r9j99p4z4</a>"},{"pid":"3c4b779e1286cc81ce134a737c8ac80e02e848c1","tid":981513,"uid":29887,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"嘩屌就咁睇相都覺得好滑"},{"pid":"df2739c632de46a2684ef687aa17248ceeec42cf","tid":981513,"uid":221748,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c4b779e1286cc81ce134a737c8ac80e02e848c1","tid":981513,"uid":29887,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"嘩屌就咁睇相都覺得好滑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"識食一定食熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baef27cbd6bb1a03898043031540b77dc7a5b9e1","tid":981513,"uid":166890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:58:00.000Z","msg":"我食過 真係好撚正"},{"pid":"9faa9db6580d279f88c042c383c8fdee04ddbcce","tid":981513,"uid":183950,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:02:40.000Z","msg":"太滑都唔係好事<br />\n隨時加左咩唔知化學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56d96e19d7feb48adf0ddb408d1d10906404ec9","tid":981513,"uid":224815,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"睇開樓主po就知佢專介紹伏野"},{"pid":"b77b43421f47ee2d9cd73fb600a909f949851493","tid":981513,"uid":221748,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9faa9db6580d279f88c042c383c8fdee04ddbcce","tid":981513,"uid":183950,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:02:40.000Z","msg":"太滑都唔係好事<br />\n隨時加左咩唔知化學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:11:31.000Z","msg":"又未滑到唔正常 果個水平既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/big